<% provide(:title, 'Home') %>

<style>
  html {
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }
  .banner_bar {
    background-color: #ddf4f2;
    padding-top: 6rem;
    padding-bottom: 6rem;
  }
  .banner_bar-text {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .banner_bar h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
  }
  .banner_bar h2 {
    font-size: 2.3rem;
  }
  .bottom_banner_bar {
    background-color: #ddf4f2;
    padding-top: 6rem;
    padding-bottom: 6rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .bottom_banner_bar p {
    font-size: 2.6rem;
  }
  .bottom_banner_bar p + p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .call_out_bar {
    background-color: #a2d7d2;
    padding-top: 8rem;
    padding-bottom: 8rem;
  }
  .call_out_bar h3 {
    font-size: 2.6rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  @media all and (max-width:40rem) {
    .call_out_bar br {
      display:none;
    }
  }

  .q-a-block {
    margin-bottom: 9rem;
  }
  .question {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 8rem;
  }
  .answer {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-top: .5rem;
  }
  .answer p {
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .perspective {
    perspective: 1500px;
    height: 14rem;
    width: 28rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-left: 2rem;
    margin-right: -2rem;
    margin-top: -5rem;
    margin-bottom: 7rem;
  }

  .cube {
    font-size: 4em;
    width: 2em;
    margin: 1.5em auto;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    transform: rotateX(-8deg) rotateY(40deg);}
    .cube:hover .banana,
    .cube:focus .banana {
      transform: rotate(-15deg);
    }
    .cube:hover .front,
    .cube:focus .front {
      transform: translateZ(1em) translateX(1.2em);
    }

  .side {
    position: absolute;
    width: 2em;
    height: 2em;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 2em;
  }

  .front  {
    transform: translateZ(1em) translateX(.4em);
    transition: transform .3s;
    background-color: #AAE2DE;
  }
  .top {
    transform: rotateX( 90deg)  translateZ(1em);
    background-color: #C3EBE9;
  }
  .right {
    transform: rotateY( 90deg) translateZ(1em);
    background-color: #4CB0A8;
  }
  .left {
    transform: rotateY(-90deg) translateZ(1em);
    background-color: #98DCD8;
  }
  .bottom {
    transform: rotateX(-90deg) translateZ(1em);
    background-color: #60BDB7;}
    .bottom:before {
      content: "";
      width: .5em;
      height: .4em;
      transform: translateY(.75em) translateX(.3em);
      background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
      position: absolute;
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: .8s infinite shrink-shadow;
    }
  .shadow {
    transform: rotateX(-90deg) translateZ(1em) translateX(-2em);
    background-color: #42948E;
  }
  .back {
    transform: rotateY(-180deg) translateZ(1em);
    background-color: #41A39B;
  }

  .banana {
    position: absolute;
    transition: transform .2s .2s;
    transform: rotate(-20deg);
    width: .9em;
    height: 1.3em;
    margin-left: 1.5em;
    margin-top: .6em;
    background-color:transparent;
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: -.2em 1px 0 -.05em rgba(0,0,0,0.1), -.4em 0 0 #ffd700;
    animation: 1.2s infinite wiggle;}
    .banana:before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      width: .1em;
      height: .2em;
      left: .2em;
      top: -.1em;
      background-color: #daa520;
      border-radius: .01em .01em .2em .1em;
      transform: rotate(66deg);
    }

  @keyframes wiggle {
    0% {
      margin-top:.6em;
    }
    50% {
      margin-top: .5em;
    }
    100% {
      margin-top:.6em;
    }
  }
  @keyframes shrink-shadow {
    0% {
      width: .5em;
      height: .4em;
    }
    50% {
      width: .4em;
      height: .3em;
    }
    100% {
      width: .5em;
      height: .4em;
    }
  }
  .tour_jumper {
    background-color: var(--teal-40);
    padding: 1.7rem 0 3.8rem;
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: black;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .tour_jumper:hover {
    background-color: var(--teal-70);
  }

  .tour_jumper:hover .icon-arrow_forward {
    animation: 1s ease-in infinite bounce;
  }

  @keyframes bounce {
    0% {
      top:3rem;
    }
    50% {
      top: 3.5rem;
    }
    100% {
      top: 3rem;
    }
  }

  .tour_jumper * {
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .tour_jumper--contents {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
  }
  .tour_jumper--contents p {
    margin-bottom: .6rem;
  }

  .tour_jumper--contents .icon-arrow_forward {
    transform: rotate(90deg);
    width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    position: absolute;
    top: 3rem;
  }

  #tour_video {
    padding: 3rem 0 5rem;
  }

  #tour_video > div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  #tour_video h3 {
    font-size: 2.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  #tour_video iframe {
    max-width: 90%;
    max-height: 55vw;
    width: 74rem;
    height: 45rem;
  }

  #tour_video a {
    background-color: var(--teal-110);
    display: block;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.7rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 2rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  #tour_video a:hover,
  #tour_video a:focus {
    background-color: var(--teal-100);
  }

</style>

<section class="banner_bar">
  <div class="standard-wrapper flex items-center flex-wrap justify-around">
    <div class="banner_bar-text">
      <h1>Stockcubes</h1>
      <h2>Fighting food waste at home</h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Attributions:

    Banana from Lynn Fisher's brilliant https://a.singlediv.com/

    Perspective cube by Hugo Giraudel. As featured on css-tricks.com
    https://css-tricks.com/almanac/properties/p/perspective/
    -->
    <div class="perspective">
      <div class="cube">
        <div class="side front"></div>
        <div class="side back"></div>
        <div class="side right"></div>
        <div class="side left"></div>
        <div class="side top"></div>
        <div class="side bottom"></div>
        <div class="side shadow"></div>
        <div class="banana"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="call_out_bar">
  <div class="standard-wrapper">
    <h3>We're here to make it ridiculously simple to <br /><strong>plan your meals</strong> and <strong>cut your food waste</strong></h3>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="tour_jumper">
  <div class="standard-wrapper tour_jumper--contents">
    <p>Check out the tour</p>
    <%= icomoon('arrow_forward') %>
  </div>
</section>


<section class="standard-wrapper q-a-block">

  <div class="question">
    <p><strong>Why should you care about food waste?</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="answer">
    <p>Well, it’s a big deal. No, really it’s massive, if you plot the emissions of food waste as it degrades, against the emissions of all the countries in the world - the only countries that produce more greenhouse gases are the US and China.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="question">
    <p><strong>But, maybe this isn’t really our problem?</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="answer">
    <p>In the UK, 6.6 Millions tonnes of food are wasted annually. We waste 70% of that total in our homes!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="question">
    <p><strong>Ok, but we’re really busy actually living our lives</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="answer">
    <p>Stockcubes wants to empower people to stop wasting food, plus there’s another benefit we haven’t mentioned yet. The dosh. The cashola. The money that you save by using your food more efficiently. In the UK, the average family would save up to £800 in a year by cutting their food waste.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="question">
    <p><strong>Right, fine, but surely it’s really difficult to solve?</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="answer">
    <p>It can be difficult, if you’re keeping track of all your food on paper and planning your meals by scouring cookbooks, but that’s where Stockcubes comes in. We’ve got delicious, simple recipes, a planner that builds you a shopping list and a recommendation engine that nudges you to use up the food you’ve already got.</p>
  </div>

</section>

<section class="bottom_banner_bar">
  <p><strong>Where do you sign up?</strong><p>
  <p>Right here: <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path %>
</section>

<section id="tour_video">
  <div class="standard-wrapper">
    <h3>Take a tour of the Stockcubes platform</h3>
    <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/puqc09GIO0I" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    <%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path %>
  </div>
</section>
